                                        <option value="rotate">각 파일 전체 회전</option>
                                        <option value="optimize">각 파일 최적화(재저장)</option>
                                    </select>
                                </label>
                                <label>회전 각도
                                    <select id="pdf-batch-rotation" class="tool-input">
                                        <option value="90">90도</option>
                                        <option value="180">180도</option>
                                        <option value="270">270도</option>
                                    </select>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="tool-actions">
                                <button type="button" class="tool-btn primary" data-action="pdf-batch-process">일괄 처리 시작</button>
                                <button type="button" class="tool-btn" data-action="pdf-batch-download">결과 다운로드</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result-grid three margin-result-grid">
                            <div><span>입력 파일</span><strong id="pdf-batch-file-count">0</strong></div>
                            <div><span>처리 페이지</span><strong id="pdf-batch-page-count">-</strong></div>
                            <div><span>결과 용량</span><strong id="pdf-batch-output-size">-</strong></div>
                        </div>
                        <ul id="pdf-batch-results" class="pdf-batch-list"></ul>
                        <p class="tool-note">파일은 브라우저에서만 처리됩니다. 여러 결과 파일은 ZIP으로 묶어 다운로드합니다. 대용량 PDF는 기기 메모리 상황에 따라 처리 시간이 길어질 수 있습니다.</p>
                    {% elseif tool.category == 'pdf' %}
                        <label for="pdf-files">PDF file{% if tool.widget == 'pdf-merge' %}s{% endif %}</label>
                        <input id="pdf-files" class="tool-input" type="file" accept="application/pdf" {% if tool.widget == 'pdf-merge' %}multiple{% endif %}>
                        {% if tool.widget == 'pdf-split' %}
                            <label for="pdf-pages">Pages</label>
                            <input id="pdf-pages" class="tool-input" type="text" placeholder="1,3-5">
                        {% elseif tool.widget == 'pdf-rotate' %}
                            <label for="pdf-rotation">Rotation</label>
                            <select id="pdf-rotation" class="tool-input">
                                <option value="90">90 degrees</option>
                                <option value="180">180 degrees</option>
                                <option value="270">270 degrees</option>
                            </select>
                        {% endif %}
                        <div class="tool-actions">
                            {% if tool.widget == 'pdf-merge' %}
                                <button type="button" class="tool-btn primary" data-action="pdf-merge">Merge PDF</button>
                            {% elseif tool.widget == 'pdf-split' %}
                                <button type="button" class="tool-btn primary" data-action="pdf-split">Split PDF</button>
                            {% elseif tool.widget == 'pdf-rotate' %}
                                <button type="button" class="tool-btn primary" data-action="pdf-rotate">Rotate PDF</button>
                            {% else %}
                                <button type="button" class="tool-btn primary" data-action="pdf-compress">Optimize PDF</button>
                            {% endif %}
                            <button type="button" class="tool-btn" data-action="pdf-download">Download</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result-grid three">
                            <div><span>Files</span><strong id="pdf-file-count">0</strong></div>
                            <div><span>Pages</span><strong id="pdf-page-count">-</strong></div>
                            <div><span>Output</span><strong id="pdf-output-size">-</strong></div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="tool-note">PDF는 브라우저에서 처리됩니다. 압축 도구는 PDF를 재저장해 불필요한 객체를 줄이는 방식이며, 스캔 이미지 압축률은 원본에 따라 달라집니다.</p>
                    {% else %}
                        <label for="tool-input">Input</label>
                        <textarea id="tool-input" class="tool-textarea" spellcheck="false" placeholder="{{ tool.name }} 기능은 단계적으로 고도화됩니다."></textarea>
                        <div class="tool-actions">
                            <button type="button" class="tool-btn primary" data-action="generic-copy">Prepare Input</button>
                            <button type="button" class="tool-btn" data-copy="#tool-output">Copy</button>
                            <button type="button" class="tool-btn" data-download="#tool-output">Download</button>
                        </div>
                        <label for="tool-output">Result</label>
                        <textarea id="tool-output" class="tool-textarea" readonly>{{ tool.name }} is registered in WY Tools. The interactive engine for this tool will be added in a later step.</textarea>
                    {% endif %}
                    <p class="tool-status" id="tool-status" aria-live="polite"></p>
                    <section class="tool-conversion-cta" aria-label="추가 서비스 안내">
                        <div class="tool-conversion-item">
                            <span>WY Tools Pro</span>
                            <h2>반복 작업을 더 빠르게 처리하세요</h2>
                            <p>대용량 처리, 저장 프리셋, 작업 기록 같은 Pro 기능이 필요하신가요?</p>
                            <a class="tool-btn primary" href="/contact?inquiry=pro&amp;tool={{ tool.slug|url_encode }}" data-premium-cta="result">Pro 대기등록</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tool-conversion-item">
                            <span>기업 자동화·구축</span>
                            <h2>이 업무를 서비스로 만들고 싶으신가요?</h2>
                            <p>반복 계산, 파일 처리, 견적·등록 업무를 맞춤형 웹 시스템으로 구축해 드립니다.</p>
                            <a class="tool-btn" href="/contact?inquiry=business&amp;tool={{ tool.slug|url_encode }}" data-business-inquiry="result">자동화 상담하기</a>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>

                {% include 'tools/partials/_ad_slot.html.twig' with { position: 'middle' } %}

                <section class="content-block">
                    <h2>사용법</h2>
                    <ol>{% for step in tool.how_to_use %}<li>{{ step }}</li>{% endfor %}</ol>
                </section>

                <section class="content-block">
                    <h2>예제</h2>
                    {% for example in tool.examples %}
                        <article class="example-card">
                            <h3>{{ example.title }}</h3>
                            <p><strong>Input:</strong> {{ example.input }}</p>
                            <p><strong>Output:</strong> {{ example.output }}</p>
                        </article>
                    {% endfor %}
                </section>

                {% for section in tool.seo_sections|default([]) %}
                    <section class="content-block seo-guide">
                        <h2>{{ section.title }}</h2>
                        <p>{{ section.content }}</p>
                    </section>
                {% endfor %}

                <section class="content-block">
                    <h2>FAQ</h2>
                    <div class="faq-list">
                        {% for faq in tool.faqs %}
                            <details><summary>{{ faq.q }}</summary><p>{{ faq.a }}</p></details>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </section>

                {% include 'tools/partials/_ad_slot.html.twig' with { position: 'after-faq' } %}

                <section class="content-block">
                    <h2>관련 도구</h2>
                    <div class="wy-tool-grid small">
                        {% for item in related_tools %}
                            {% include 'tools/partials/_tool_card.html.twig' with { item: item, card_context: 'related', source_tool: tool.slug } %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </section>
            </main>

            <aside class="tool-sidebar">
                <div class="help-box">
                    <h2>도구 정보</h2>
                    <p>{{ tool.summary }}</p>
                    {% if tool.view_count is defined and tool.view_count > 0 %}
                        <p class="tool-views">{{ tool.view_count|number_format }} views</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if tool.updated_at is defined %}<p class="tool-updated">업데이트: {{ tool.updated_at }}</p>{% endif %}
                    <a href="/tools/category/{{ tool.category }}">{{ category.name|default(tool.category) }} Tools</a>
                </div>
                <div class="help-box">
                    <h2>최근 사용</h2>
                    <div class="compact-list" data-recent-tools></div>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </section>

    {% include 'tools/partials/_ad_slot.html.twig' with { position: 'footer' } %}
</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
    {% if tool.widget == 'qr-code' %}
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/qrcodejs@1.0.0/qrcode.min.js"></script>
    {% endif %}
    {% if tool.category == 'pdf' %}
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/pdf-lib@1.17.1/dist/pdf-lib.min.js"></script>
    {% endif %}
    {% if tool.widget == 'pdf-batch' %}
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jszip@3.10.1/dist/jszip.min.js"></script>
    {% endif %}
    <script src="/assets/js/tools.js"></script>
{% endblock %}
